{"tid":1427209,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【以正視聽】光復香港 時代革命既由來同意義","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:05.000Z","uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"971ba31dd2ed393d68b4429a461e9e246b84e16c","tid":1427209,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"梁天琦三年前角逐立法會新界東補選，時任選舉經理人何蔓兒在fb稱，梁最初以「知行合一，世代革新」為選舉口號，但後來覺得口號「唔夠搶耳」，就借用2015年屯門、上水等光復行動的口號，放大到「光復香港」，提醒選民其所屬政黨本土民主前線是在街頭抗爭爭取香港人應有權利的抗爭者。<br />\n至於「革命」一詞，何解釋，二字切合本民前的政治理念，「最後天琦思前想後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">覺得革新同改變唔係取決於人嘅年齡，而係取決於人嘅思想有冇追上時代嘅步伐</span></span>，所以決定以『光復香港，時代革命』作為選舉口號」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地俾柒婆老屈點解係要撒回口處，而唔係向我地所有同路人解釋真正意思？<br />\n當大家都了解到呢句口號既意思，就知道呢句係團結緊所有香港人，所以不滿政府既人，所有真正追求民主既人<br />\n革新/改革唔係取決於年齡，而係所有人思上追上時代既步伐<br />\n香港唔止屬於後生仔，仲係遲於中年人，老年人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梁天琦，你真係好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f816e1d2f95ee0aaebcdde6c9f2d5cb660c56a98","tid":1427209,"uid":148960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n[綜合討論] 目前運動出現嘅問題以至未來方向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dydHsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dydHsS</a>"},{"pid":"c414e39f30e29b9d2049fa89dfca471fcf06327d","tid":1427209,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff359645ca3557e39efcc6574053aadf8de00f8","tid":1427209,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbeced01642dfeea71d7824fd07e94c6dedc21b","tid":1427209,"uid":64614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"李怡都提出咗光復香港，時代革命嘅新解釋！<br />\n光復香港，就是要光復到人權有保障、市民有法律權利、警察是保護市民而不是向自由表達意見的市民施暴的香港！即係四大訴求！<br />\n時代革命，就是要把被中共港共徹底破壞了的一國兩制、港人治港作根本性的改變。即係要撥亂反正！要有基本法承諾嘅雙普選！<br />\n<br />\n要睇李怡先生篇文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/575891235797924/posts/2420289171358112?s=686974489&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F575891235797924%2Fposts%2F2420289171358112%3Fs%3D686974489%26sfns%3Dmo&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z60GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=52b6b0f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/575891235797924/posts/2420289171358112?s=686974489&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好成日怕俾位人入！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"c40cd30a28bb363d4f408b7d9bf6096c64f32881","tid":1427209,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"其他口號用字不夠好﹐不夠力﹐革命 用字 代表人民對運動抗爭的立場最堅定不移﹐絕對不會退縮﹐和獨是完全沒有關係。<br />\n你用革命二字﹐只代表你非常堅定做事｡"},{"pid":"07727454c6eb891a250c05874bc107f1d0be8e53","tid":1427209,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQoazRf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQoazRf.png&h=236cac31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2cKEhW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2cKEhW.jpg&h=53f4ae80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRGfLXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRGfLXW.jpg&h=a6020ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wG2R3KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwG2R3KC.jpg&h=ba33973f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6f1579f4dacabb74f2871de3738ead86136264